OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrit Awards tweak rules    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter diversity row        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Organisers of the Brit Awards have     
OL,6, announced they will update their rules 
OL,7, to address criticism over diversity.   
OL,9,FThe show faced a backlash in January   
OL,10,Fwhen it was revealed that no women were
OL,11,Fshortlisted for the best artist prize, 
OL,12,Fwhich replaced the gendered best male  
OL,13,Fand female categories two years ago.   
OL,15,FHarry Styles, who won the award,       
OL,16,Fdedicated it to artists like Charli    
OL,17,FXCX, who had been overlooked.          
OL,19,FThe Brits will now expand the number of
OL,20,Fnominees for the prize from five to 10.
